3. RECIPROCAL DISCLOSURE (THE ALGORITHM MANDATE)
If you use this Software, or any portion thereof, for any Commercial Purpose, you MUST publicly disclose the full logic and source code of your own integrated or derivative trading algorithms to a public repository.
- "Commercial Purpose" includes, but is not limited to, using the software for high-frequency trading, proprietary fund management, or as part of a paid service.
- Disclosure must be made in a machine-readable format within 30 days of commercial activation.

4. PERPETUITY
The Reciprocal Disclosure requirement is perpetual. Even if you cease using the Software or rewrite your own logic, the obligation to maintain the public disclosure of the algorithm that utilized PQR remains in effect.

